Revision history for Perl extension CmdArgs.

0.8.0:
  + add support of ~OPT.
  + add tests.
  + add options groups sorting in help message.
  + change the required perl version to v5.10.
  + change documentation.
  + fix error check.

0.7.0:
  + add support of ~mopt? in the use case specification.
  + add ignoring of options permutations in the use case.
  + add constant $CmdArgs::DEBUG_LEVEL to control debug messages.
  + add more error checks.
  + add more tests.
  + add t/lib/CmdArgsTest.pm as the container for common test functions.
  + fix error in redeclaration after failure.
  + fix resolution of ambiguous GROUP GROUP case.
  + fix missing suitable cases.
  + fix perf_test.pl.

0.6.1:
  + fix to reset '--' state for each parse_part invocation.

0.6.0:
  + add arguments partial parsing.
  + add method parse_begin.
  + add method parse_part.
  + add method parse_end.
  + fix the using of an empy group.

0.5.1:
  + fix the case 'mopt after arg' for any-place-options.

0.5.0:
  + add any-place options.
  + add PositiveInt and NonnegativeInt to BasicTypes.
  + add t/any_place_otps.t.
  + add t/basic_types.t.

0.4.0:
  + add CmdArgs/BasicTypes.pm.
  + add restrictions.
  + add customizable help message generation system.
  + add static use case for CmdArgs.
  + add expressions in a group specification, e.g. qw(* ^opt ^ABOUT).
  + add ability to specify option argument name.
  + add ability to specify a variable reference instead of option's action subroutine.
  + add ability to have options with the single '-', e.g. '-option'.
  + add ability to set options this way: 'option=value'.
  + add ability to enable debugging messages.
  + add setting of local $_ variable in option's action subroutine.
  + add an arrangement of options in the group 'OPTIONS' by the first key.
  + add new default group ABOUT.
  + add export function ptext.
  + add method opt_or_default.
  + add method set_help_params.
  + add method get_help_params.
  + add method usage_custom_usecases.
  + add method help_custom_usecases.
  + add method help_custom_groups_filter.
  + add method help_custom_group_name.
  + add method help_custom_options_filter.
  + add method help_custom_option.
  + add method m_update_teminal_info.
  + add method m_usecases_to_str.
  + add function m_format_text.
  + add function m_split_text.
  + add function m_smart_split_by_width.
  + add more tests.
  + add performance test perf_test.pl.
  + change to hide _GROUPS in help message.
  + change the group for HELP and VERSION options to ABOUT.
  + change location of arrangement data to $self->{arrangement}.
  + change $self->{use_cases_order} to $self->{arrangement}{use_cases}.
  + change error messages for failed checks of typed arguments.
  + change HELP and VERSION options descriptions.
  + change method m_usage_message.
  + change method m_help_message.
  + fix documentation.
  + fix error messages.
  + fix to print specified key in error message instead of option name.

0.3.0:
  + fixed help and usage messages.
  + options action
  + hiden options
  + arrange use_cases
  + fixed some bugs
